ApplicationItem.description: The Application Item associated with the Individual Application Task Item.

ApplicationItemType.description: The type of Application Item associated with the Individual Application Task Item.

IndividualApplicationTaskId.description: The Individual Application Task associated with the Individual Application Task Item.

LastReferencedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last accessed this record, a record related to this record, or a list view.

LastViewedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last viewed this record or list view. If this value is null, the user might have only accessed this record or list view (LastReferencedDate) but not viewed it.

SequenceNumber.description: The sequence number of the individual application task item.
